msgstr "Beräkningsmetod för kortaste avstånd Möjliga värden är:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1520
msgid "0 --- Distance to nearest point on feature"
msgstr "0 --- Avstånd till närmaste punkt på objektet"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1521
msgid "1 --- Distance to feature centroid"
msgstr "1 --- Avstånd till objektets tyngdpunkt"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1523
msgid "**Maximum number of neighbors**"
msgstr "**Maximalt antal grannar**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1524
msgid "``NEIGHBORS``"
msgstr "``NEIGHBORS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1527
msgid "Default: 1"
msgstr "Standard: 1"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1528
msgid "Maximum number of neighbors to look for"
msgstr "Maximalt antal grannar att leta efter"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1529
msgid "**Maximum distance**"
msgstr "**Maximalt avstånd**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1532
msgid "``DISTANCE``"
msgstr "``DISTANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1534
msgid ""
"Only destination features which are closer than this distance will be "
"considered."
msgstr ""
"Endast destinationsfunktioner som ligger närmare än detta avstånd kommer att"
" beaktas."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1536
msgid "**Shortest lines**"
msgstr "**Kortaste linjerna**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1559
msgid "**Output layer**"
msgstr "**Utmatningslager**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1562
msgid ""
"Line vector layer joining source features to their nearest neighbor(s) in "
"the destination layer. Contains all attributes for both source and "
"destination features, and the computed distance."
msgstr ""
"Linjevektorlager som sammanfogar källfunktioner med deras närmaste granne(r)"
" i destinationslagret. Innehåller alla attribut för både käll- och "
"destinationsobjekten samt det beräknade avståndet."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1569
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:shortestline``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-id**: ``native:shortestline``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1579
msgid "ST-DBSCAN clustering"
msgstr "ST-DBSCAN klustring"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1581
msgid ""
"Clusters point features based on a 2D implementation of spatiotemporal "
"Density-based clustering of applications with noise (ST-DBSCAN) algorithm."
msgstr ""
"Klustrar punktfunktioner baserat på en 2D-implementering av spatiotemporal "
"Density-based clustering of applications with noise (ST-DBSCAN)-algoritm."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1584
